Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.63,0:00:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲太郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.98,0:00:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.40,0:00:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.44,0:00:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须有人留在这里殿后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.80,0:00:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然不论胜败我们将无一幸存
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.78,0:00:24.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧 一旦处于劣势我就会逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.97,0:00:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将监先生就交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.30,0:00:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.56,0:00:29.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走 延珠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.18,0:02:22.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,400)\pos(655,388)\fsp4\bord0}#04 黑色的子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.78,0:02:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是安静呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.47,0:02:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.07,0:02:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.40,0:02:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.24,0:02:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的剑在哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.78,0:02:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是伊熊将监吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我的剑在哪里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有…那个的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:56.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就能…继续战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 真让人吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然真的还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时候就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来做个了断吧 里见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.87,0:03:19.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附近的民警搭档 就算是最近的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要花费一个小时以上才能赶到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.78,0:03:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木更
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我叫她来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天童社长 你认为里见搭档胜算如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以加上我个人的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.58,0:03:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为绝对会赢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？对方可是「新人类创造计划」的幸存者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.48,0:03:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能有胜算…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.47,0:03:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年前 原肠动物侵入我家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.47,0:03:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(413,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吞杀了家父与家母
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那时的压力 我的肾脏机能基本上都停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.54,0:04:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时 里见莲太郎为了保护我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被原肠动物夺去了右手 右腿和左眼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(285,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,濒死的他被送到了二十二局
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.03,0:04:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主刀医生是室户堇医师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,室户堇？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是拿不回箱子的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有我们阻挡在你的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两次败北 同伴全灭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 真是求之不得啊 你这混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要干掉你！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天童式战斗术一型三号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「辘轳鹿伏鬼」！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然打破了「最强之痛」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然是錵的义肢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(423,437)\fs21}Varanium
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要自报家门了 影胤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是前陆上自卫队东部方面队第七八七机械化特殊部队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.41,0:05:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「新人类创造计划」 里见莲太郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.88,0:05:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来还有另外一个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.40,0:05:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原肠动物战争孕育的人类武器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.40,0:05:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(289.5,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很痛…我还活着…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美好的人生！哈利路亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别欺负我爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.18,0:06:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哭泣吧Sodomy 歌唱吧Gospel
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们仅仅是为了杀戮而被创造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果原肠动物战争再次开始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(363,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能证明我们的存在意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你这家伙仅仅是为了这个目的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你的起始者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(467,437)\fs21}Initiator
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.67,0:06:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那被诅咒的孩子身份暴露时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周围的反应如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:31.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她受到祝福了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:35.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心灵被经久不息的欢呼声净化了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们和我们所希望的世界是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是被选中的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 里见莲太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.16,0:06:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了 你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.44,0:06:53.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所说的未来 我绝对不能容许
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,延珠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不服从我的话 就去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:22.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你输了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…要死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,延…珠…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲太郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.86,0:07:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别把人家一个人丢下！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:45.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AGV实验性药物 是用原肠动物的病毒制成的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:45.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(468,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然能给予人类原肠动物般的再生能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(437,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也会有20%的概率原肠动物化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(537,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以的话最好别用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲…莲太郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.04,0:08:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赌赢了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:37.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里见…你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.09,0:08:43.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天童式战斗术「水天一碧架势」！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「云岭毗湖鲤鲋」！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「隐禅·哭汀」！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.00,0:09:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我输给你了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸… 爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛭子影胤的反应消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.52,0:09:31.30,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.16,0:09:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她已经不是敌人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我遵守约定赢了 木更小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.44,0:10:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.53,0:10:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 里见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个坏消息必须告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阶段Ⅴ的原肠动物现身了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(437,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:10:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.54,0:11:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不能让一切结束
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.11,0:11:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的作战已经得到了圣天子大人的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案就在你的东南方向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「天梯」…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由你来做 里见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,线形超电磁投射装置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别名「天梯」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直径800毫米以下的金属飞行物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加速到亚光速射出的磁轨炮模块
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:41.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果以它无法躲避的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将錵子弹射入
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(377,437)\fs21}Varanium
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是阶段Ⅴ的原肠动物也一定能消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(437,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,线形超电磁投射装置开始启动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.53,0:11:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电力供给没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.64,0:12:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保存液态氦的杜瓦瓶也没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 里见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:06.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,启动后的发动程序全部由我们这边执行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:08.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就只要看着就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除此之外我们也无能为力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是阶段Ⅴ吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 黄道带原肠动物·天蝎座
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(439,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经将世界逼至毁灭边缘的原肠动物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(600,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:12:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里见 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,系统显示炮膛位置异常
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.04,0:13:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是因为没有填充錵制穿甲弹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.04,0:13:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(498,437)\fs21}Varanium
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 没有子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:24.35,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,电力储存系统的冷却剂外泄 请立刻停止实验
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 莲太郎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:27.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为磁场的影响…里见…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们无法进行远程输入 里见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.72,0:13:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲太郎…难道你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把手臂当成子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是超錵应该没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(394,437)\fs21}Varanium
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錵填充确认
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(364,437)\fs21}Varanium
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.43,0:14:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射击管制装置依然无法修复
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.77,0:14:06.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除在管制室手动射击外别无他法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.79,0:14:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里见 你听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:10.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这边无法射出磁轨炮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.01,0:14:12.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了 由你来发射吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等…你在开玩笑吧 木更小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.34,0:14:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到啊 木更小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.63,0:14:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里见 请…拯救…世…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木更小姐 木更小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能量充填率100% 启动手动扳机控制系统
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.40,0:14:34.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲太郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.06,0:14:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依靠手动能击中距离五十公里外的目标吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.47,0:14:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.36,0:14:56.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里见先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲太郎 人家就在你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如…如果我射偏了 我们就都完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会击中的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.77,0:15:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一子弹偏离轨道击中东京区域
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会带来前所未有的大灾难
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.98,0:15:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 莲太郎你一定能击中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.35,0:15:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,延珠…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有莲太郎能拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.87,0:15:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是其他任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有莲太郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.16,0:16:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,延珠 我绝对不想失去你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那句话人家可以解释为求婚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 只是作为家人的担忧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十岁小鬼谈什么恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.68,0:16:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不害怕了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我会结束这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,延珠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:43.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么没有逃走？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.36,0:18:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…被抓住了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说过 一旦陷入劣势就会逃走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里见先生 将监先生呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.10,0:18:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.42,0:18:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里见先生 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.82,0:18:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没错 侵蚀率已经超过50%了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我以人的姿态死去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.74,0:18:39.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定了我的存在 我不想让你死去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我尽力了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.00,0:18:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我能活着真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我的心中充满了感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.63,0:19:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里见先生没什么朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.95,0:19:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来做你的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我无可替代的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里见先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.41,0:19:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你以后迷失在黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请遵从自己心中的指南针
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向着光明的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救这个世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.88,0:20:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情报被泄露给影胤这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经以辔田防卫大臣单方面的失控作结
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辔田刚才在看守所上吊自杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.85,0:20:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人是你的部下吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原肠动物新法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(393,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.46,0:20:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了提高被诅咒的孩子社会地位的法案
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.65,0:20:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你却是个顽固的歧视主义者！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.65,0:20:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公开宣布影胤的女儿小比奈与这次恐怖事件有关联
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要让人们对被诅咒的孩子产生反感！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.25,0:20:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了阻止原肠动物新法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.25,0:20:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(451,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.58,0:20:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至企图召唤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.77,0:20:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能使整个东京区域大灭绝的阶段Ⅴ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.30,0:20:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么能够忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年前 我的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.87,0:20:56.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都被屠杀的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:20:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那群小鬼继承了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.56,0:21:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺去了你的手脚和父母的蝼蚁的血
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.71,0:21:04.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你却想给予她们人权？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们才是毁灭整个世界的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.01,0:21:12.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:16.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 里见莲太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信蓝原延珠！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.78,0:21:21.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙……
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.00,0:21:25.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.56,0:21:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不想死的话就活下去 莲太郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.62,0:21:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我因绝望而闭上双眼的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.21,0:21:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起了那句话 挺了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年前的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一刻未曾忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.66,0:21:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣天子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.18,0:21:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有件事想要请教
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.30,0:21:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.49,0:21:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了箱子里的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坏掉的三轮车
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.04,0:22:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它为什么会成为召唤天蝎座的触媒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.91,0:22:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原肠动物到底是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.91,0:22:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(334,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.30,0:22:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请告诉我 圣天子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.42,0:22:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于此事 我无可奉告
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.59,0:22:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲太郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.53,0:22:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 手臂已经痊愈了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.76,0:22:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.15,0:22:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从菫那里知道人家的侵蚀率检查的结果了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.08,0:22:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是24.9%
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.06,0:22:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 几乎没什么变化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.53,0:22:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里见先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.86,0:22:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果排名上升的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.64,0:22:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,民警搭档将会被授予特权
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.83,0:22:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虚拟阶级的提升
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.93,0:23:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有机密情报的通行钥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.64,0:23:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里见先生 你要和延珠小姐提升排名等级
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.54,0:23:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那时 你便会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.57,0:23:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己是谁 为了什么出生在这世上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.48,0:23:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}诊断报告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.48,0:23:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}侵蚀率 42.1%
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.48,0:23:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}形象崩溃预测值
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.48,0:23:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}剩余 7.2%
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.99,0:23:50.02,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fsp4\be4\bord2}#05  红黑色的暗杀者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.53,0:23:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有委托
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.60,0:23:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内容是护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.31,0:23:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲太郎 人家有种不好的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.54,0:23:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.83,0:23:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的任务是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.14,0:23:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除掉东京区域的代表圣天子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OP
